   RReeggiisstteerrss
       Formatting  distances can be controlled in -mm by means of
       built-in number registers.  For  example,  this  sets  the
       line length to 6.5 inches: .nr  LL  6.5i

       Here is a table of number registers and their default val-
       ues:
       ------------------------------------------------------
       Name     Explanation
       ------------------------------------------------------
       _CC_ll       Heading Levels in Table of Contents
       _DD_ss       Vertical Space surrounding displays
       _EE_cc       Equation caption Count
       _EE_jj       Determines New Page for headings
       _EE_xx       Exhibit caption count
       _FF_gg       Figure Caption Count
       _FF_ss       Separation between footnotes
       _HH_11       Controls First Level Heading Numbers
       _HH_22       Controls Second Level Heading Numbers
       _HH_33       Controls Third Level Heading Numbers
       _HH_44       Controls Fourth Level Heading Numbers
       _HH_55       Controls Fifth Level Heading Numbers
       _HH_66       Controls Sixth Level Heading Numbers
       _HH_77       Controls Seventh Level Heading Numbers
       _HH_bb       Heading Break Level
       _HH_cc       Determine Centering of Headings
       _HH_ii       Post Heading Indent
       _HH_ss       Heading Space level
       _HH_tt       Controls Concatenation of subsection numbers
       _LL_ee       Set Inclusion of equations in T of C
       _LL_ff       Set Inclusion of figures in T of C
       _LL_ii       List indentation
       _LL_tt       Set Inclusion of tables in T of C
       _LL_xx       Set Inclusion of exhibits in T of C
       _NN_pp       Paragraph Numbering Style
       _PP_ii       Paragraph Indentation
       _PP_ss       Point size
       _PP_tt       Paragraph Style
       _PP_vv       Controls "Private" message on document
       _RR_ff       Current Reference Number
       _SS_ii       Indentation of displays
       _TT_bb       Table Caption Count

