       --------------------------------------------------------------------------------
       Name      String's Function
       --------------------------------------------------------------------------------
       _\\_**_((_BB_UU     automatically produces a bullet
       _\\_**_((_EE_MM     dash
       _\\_**_((_DD_TT     current date in the form "month,day,year"
       _\\_**_((_TT_mm     trademark (places the letters TM half a line above preceding text and

